code: @Test public void testHasExistingTemplate() {     assertNotNull("Should have injected a consumer template", template).     ConsumerTemplate lookup = context.getRegistry().lookupByNameAndType("myConsumerTemplate", ConsumerTemplate.class).     assertNotNull("Should lookup consumer template", lookup).     ConsumerTemplate lookup2 = context.getRegistry().lookupByNameAndType("consumerTemplate", ConsumerTemplate.class).     assertNull("Should not be able to lookup consumer template", lookup2). }

@Test public void testShouldBeSingleton() {     ConsumerTemplate lookup = context.getRegistry().lookupByNameAndType("myConsumerTemplate", ConsumerTemplate.class).     assertNotNull("Should lookup producer template", lookup).     ConsumerTemplate lookup2 = context.getRegistry().lookupByNameAndType("myConsumerTemplate", ConsumerTemplate.class).     assertNotNull("Should lookup producer template", lookup).     assertSame("Should be same instances (singleton)", lookup, lookup2). }
